with this one?

1080
01:19:21,040 --> 01:19:22,360
Max and Wyatt!

1081
01:19:22,440 --> 01:19:23,520
We should call them some time.

1082
01:19:23,600 --> 01:19:25,880
Honey, I think 
we cost them enough trouble.

1083
01:19:26,560 --> 01:19:28,120
I can't wait 
for the next summer break.

1084
01:19:28,200 --> 01:19:29,600
You'll come with us, right, Grandpa?

1085
01:19:29,680 --> 01:19:31,680
- You got it, Sammy. 
- I miss that ball pit.

1086
01:19:31,760 --> 01:19:32,960
Hey, look at that.

1087
01:19:33,440 --> 01:19:34,680
I don't even remember that.

1088
01:19:34,760 --> 01:19:36,000
- Did you take that? 
- Yeah.

1089
01:19:36,080 --> 01:19:37,600
That's really good.

1090
01:19:37,680 --> 01:19:38,880
You could be a pro photographer.

1091
01:19:38,960 --> 01:19:40,120
Yeah, I know. I'm shocked.
